headline: Deel eyes more acquisitions after hitting $1 billion annual revenue run rate
summary: Payroll startup Deel said on Tuesday it crossed $1 billion annualrevenue run rate in the first quarter and has earmarked up to $500 million for acquisitions thisyear to bolster growth. ...
